title: Aliases kept to prevent broken links
content: This section contains a few aliases that we temporarily keep to prevent broken links. If you land on any of these, please let the originating site and/or us know that the link that made you land here should be changed.

blocks.name: dummylink
blocks.content: Alias for ~ a1ii that may be referenced in some older works, and kept here to prevent broken links. If you landed here, please let the originating site and/or us know that the link that made you land here should be changed to a link to ~ a1ii . (Contributed by NM, 7-Feb-2006.) (Proof modification is discouraged.) (New usage is discouraged.)
